OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FA new train service will soon offer
OL,8,Fpassengers another way to reach London
OL,9,Ffrom Carlisle.
OL,11,FLumo Trains will start its Stirling to
OL,12,FLondon Euston service on 25 May,
OL,13,Fstopping in our region at Lockerbie
OL,14,Fand Carlisle.
OL,16,FThe operator promises cheaper fares,
OL,17,Fwith luggage restrictions and no first
OL,18,Fclass carriages helping to reduce
OL,19,Fprices.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
