PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FHere's what you need to know about the
OL,8,Fnew service:
OL,10,FWhere will this service call? This new
OL,11,Froute begins at Stirling and ends at
OL,12,FLondon Euston.
OL,14,FOn the way, Lumo trains will stop at
OL,15,FLarbert, Greenfaulds, Whifflet,
OL,16,FMotherwell, Lockerbie, Carlisle,
OL,17,FPreston, Crewe, Nuneaton, and Milton
OL,18,FKeynes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FThis means that in our region, you can
OL,8,Fonly board a Lumo train at Lockerbie
OL,9,For Carlisle.
OL,11,FHow frequently will this service run
OL,12,Ffrom Carlisle? Lumo says that when the
OL,13,Ffinal timetable comes into effect,
OL,14,Fthere will be four daily return
OL,15,Fservices from Stirling to London,
OL,16,Fstopping at Carlisle, with an
OL,17,Fadditional service running between
OL,18,FPreston and London Euston.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
