OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FWhen can I catch a Lumo train? The
OL,8,FLumo Trains website says that limited
OL,9,FStirling to London Euston services
OL,10,Fwill go on sale from 25 May, with a
OL,11,Ffull timetable available on 27 July.
OL,13,FAt first, between May 25 and June 18,
OL,14,Fthere will be one southbound and one
OL,15,Fnorthbound service.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FFrom 19 June to 4 July, there will be
OL,8,Ftwo services in each direction daily,
OL,9,Fapart from on Sundays, when there will
OL,10,Fbe only one southbound service from
OL,11,FStirling, but two northbound services
OL,12,Ffrom London.
OL,14,FThe full timetable with four daily
OL,15,Fservices will commence from 27 July.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
