FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FCan I take luggage with me? Unlike
OL,8,Fmost rail services, Lumo trains have
OL,9,Fbaggage restrictions. Customers may
OL,10,Fbring on board a maximum of one small
OL,11,Fbag and one medium suitcase - defined
OL,12,Fas not exceeding 63 x 41 x 27cm.
OL,14,FIs there a fine for bringing more
OL,15,Fluggage? There is. Luggage that
OL,16,Fexceeds the above limits will be
OL,17,Fcharged at #40 per item - or customers
OL,18,Fcould even be refused travel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
