PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779639072
OL,3,CNew 'cheaper' train service from
OL,4,CCarlisle to Preston: What you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FWhat even is Lumo? Lumo Trains is an
OL,8,F'open-access' train operator, which
OL,9,Fmeans it runs on infrastructure owned
OL,10,Fby a third party, and that Lumo will
OL,11,Ftake on full commercial risk for the
OL,12,Fservice - this means that it is not
OL,13,Ffranchised by or subsidised by the
OL,14,FGovernment.
OL,16,FLumo already operates services on the
OL,17,FEast Coast Main Line, running from
OL,18,FLondon King's Cross to Edinburgh
OL,19,FWaverley and Glasgow Queen Street.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
